<font color= "brown" size= +1>Material, sources </font> 


<p>Special Relativity challenges our intuition and takes effort to
digest; so I strongly suggest trying to read a fair bit every week.

<p>For example, you could aim to work through two sections of
Nash's notes (below) every week, or a similar amount of work from
another text.


<p><br>
